definitions.definition: Extroverted : talkative , friendly , and social , especially with respect to meeting new people easily and comfortably .
examples: Tom is very outgoing and enjoys meeting people; his brother, on the other hand, is painfully shy.

definitions.definition: Going out, on its way out.
Being replaced in office (while still in office but after election has determined that he/she will be replaced).
examples: The outgoing politician wasn't too disappointed he'd lost the election; he was tired of political infighting.
